checker.matching
Class DiffAnalysis

java.lang.Object
  checker.matching.DiffAnalysis

public class DiffAnalysis
extends java.lang.Object

License match analysis. This class analyzes the results of matching comments to a license template with the Diff class.

Author:
Lauri Koponen

Class constructor that analyzes the Diff result. Results are stored in the DiffAnalysis instance and can be retrieved with member methods.

Parameters:
diff - Diff to be analysed
template - license template used in matching
text - comments used in matching
minMatch - Minimum matched substring length, percentage of total length in range 0.0 .. 1.0
